Author: bubblyqueer
Text: Thank you. I totally get you. We can try to trick ourselves and say we are fine and this isn’t doing anything to us and we will stop when x. But you and I both know that’s just how we keep ourselves trapped by denying the damage we are doing and how miserable we are. I hope that you get the help you need and are able to kick ed in the ass

Author: DesperateLyingFox
Text: >July 1st, I’m going to treatment. Even if it means I have to be tubed before then.  I wish you good luck and strength. I feel the same with everything you wrote. Its basically slowly killing me. My body and my mind...
